lines: 1. Ruoth En E Jakwadha, orita maber;Lum mang`ich omiya, oruaka e kunde;Oteloni chunya kar pige mokuwe;Oduoga kabayo, ohoyo chuny mang`ich.
2. Kayudo masira kata tho malich,Nikech In mirita,Ok naluor gimoro;Igeng`a gi ludhi kod odungani;Gima rach ok nyala ka Jakony ni buta.
3. Ipedhona mesa ndalo mar chandruok;Imiya gweth mang`eny ma onge kar giko;Iolona mo mang`we ng`ar e wiya;Ng`wononi mogundho omako dhoga chuth.
4. Ng`wononi gi berni, Nyasacha maber;Mondo luwre koda nyak` achop iri ku;Nalu yorno ma jo machon noluwo,Nyak` adonji kanyo, pinyruodhi mar hera.
